node.text: To me progression is ... evolving as an artist ... as a father ... as a skier ... Alaska has been a direct source of inspiration for my evolution. It’s a place where every aspect draws me in. A place that ultimately tests my creativity and patience. From line choice to the overall geographical phenomena that shapes those mountains and allows snow to cling to vertical faces. Each time I go I have to push past mental and physical boundaries, and when the stars align, even if only for a day, I feel that I enter a new dimension within. Thank you @dakine for getting me back up to Haines, where it all started 15 years ago with a few of my heroes • One who is no longer with us #weloveyoujp • We had a 24 hour window before the world went on lockdown, and were able to create this passion piece with the help of @dakine & @flagshipindependent. Hope you enjoy it —» Progression is: AN EVOLUTION • Full edit also available on DAKINE YouTube • @dakine_ski
